I live in a big city. My neighborhood is very diverse. Many different kinds of buildings are here. Homes and offices are near stores and restaurants. There are many places to eat and shop. Some stores are big and well-known. Others are small and unique. They are in malls or on streets. These streets are near quiet neighborhoods. But they are not quiet because of the many interesting places.

There are parks near my home. Many people visit these parks with their young children. My neighborhood has many different kinds of people. There is a big LGBTQ+ community. There are also Orthodox Jews and people from the former Soviet Union. Many other people from different countries live in the city. Some live in areas like Korea Town, China Town, and Little Armenia.

But getting around the city is difficult. It takes a long time to drive just a few miles. This is because of traffic. Most people do not walk in the city. We have a lot of cars, and it is hard to find places to park. The city is building more buildings. This means more people will come and drive. Some people do not like this.

There are many kinds of homes in the city. Not everyone lives in big buildings. Some people live in houses or small apartments. My neighborhood is the same. There are many different kinds of homes. People of all ages live here. I do not know most of my neighbors. But I have good memories of playing with friends when I was a child.

My neighborhood is interesting. It has single-family homes. Some homes are attached, but still separate. My home has a small yard and a small driveway. Most homes look like they did many years ago. That was when living in the suburbs was the American dream. Many people still like our neighborhood. They like the homes and the way it looks. But people are not as happy as they used to be. The yards are not kept up well. But there are still cars in every driveway. Children play outside as if the world is all they have. We have a school that has been here for almost 90 years. It still looks good and makes young people think about the future. Older people remember the good old days when they were young. We have a few churches, but they are not used much. The basketball courts are still busy. All the homes look different, but feel the same. There is a big store called Super A. It is owned by a Yemeni family. They are probably the only Arab family in our neighborhood. Most people in our neighborhood are African American. Our streets are wide and children play football. Most people have lived here for a long time. They can tell stories of when everyone knew each other. There used to be a karate school, but it closed. Now it is a pharmacy. People think medicine makes everything better. We have a small movie theater that shows old movies at a low price. Young people do not like it because it does not have new movies. Older people like it because it is cheap and a good way to go out. We have a highway that goes through our town. But the entrance and exit are in the next town. Some people wanted a highway exit in our town, but others did not. They said it would hurt our town. The town council agreed with them. We are getting a new high school. We are trying to decide on a name for it. I think a cyborg with a country accent and a log cabin would be a good name for our town.

You might not notice it at first. It is a residential area behind a shopping strip. Not a place people usually want to live. But if you walk behind the old, abandoned store, you will find a community. 

The community has apartment buildings. They are next to each other. These buildings are like connected houses. The first apartments you see have been in the news for bad things. We will not talk about them too much. But the other buildings are a different story. Almost no one knows about this part of the community.

Across from these buildings is a school. It is a small college. Students go there to learn. They arrive in the morning with coffee and yawn. The gates open slowly. Commuters get angry because the students cause traffic.

A road meets another road here. On one side is a park. On the other side is a place to help people with broken bones. The center has comfortable chairs and a fan that moves the air. Children play in the park. They run and play with their friends. Old people walk their dogs and look at the teenagers on their skateboards.

There is a store with cheap food. There is a store for swimming pools. There is a place for people to get their nails done. You can fill your pool while getting food and a manicure. There is a store for frozen yogurt. Teenagers eat cold yogurt and do tricks on their skateboards.

This neighborhood is a part of America. It is a place with a lot of history. Not much changes here. Time seems to go slowly.

She looked out the window and asked, "Where are we?" The fields of corn stretched far out. "This is it," I said. She looked surprised. She was from a town where the grocery store was close to her house. She had never seen so much open space. I told her what it was like to grow up in a small town in Ohio. She finally understood who I was.

We drove down a country road. There was a big hole in the ground filled with water. Just past it was my neighborhood. The houses were made of brick and stucco. Each house had a lot of land. People take care of their land. In the spring, flowers and trees are beautiful. The driveways have expensive cars. My Korean neighbor is always outside. He mows his lawn and sings. Everyone likes him. He is a kind person. He used to be a doctor. Now he is older and sometimes forgetful.

As we drove, you will see my house. There are geese in the yard. Our dog chases them. Behind my house is a stream. You can hear the water, frogs, and sometimes cows from the farms. A bridge made of wood leads to a special place. There are trees, herbs, and flowers that grow naturally. This is where I spent most of my childhood. I built forts and played with my friends.

In the winter, it can be very cold. But it is also beautiful. The trees look bare and the yard is empty. Sometimes it snows and the yard looks like a winter wonderland. My little sister and I would make snow angels and snowmen. We would fight and use snowballs as weapons. We built forts made of branches. We would play pretend and forget about everything else.

Portland is a city in Oregon. It is famous for being weird. The city's unofficial slogan is "Keep Portland Weird." This means the city is different from other places. Some people think this is good. They see it as a fun and creative place. Others think it is a call to come and visit. They will not be judged for being different. 

The city has changed. Many rich people from California have moved here. They have built new homes. Some people are not happy about this change. But Portland is still a weird place. It accepts things that other places do not. The city has modern things like everyone else. People buy things from China. In Portland, you can find many different kinds of people. There are business people, artists, and people who like yoga. The city has colorful houses and gardens. There are free boxes on the street. These boxes have things that people are getting rid of. You never know what you might find. It is like a treasure hunt.

Not everyone likes Portland. Some people do not want to take things from the street. They go to special events like goat yoga. This is a kind of yoga with real goats. Others go to soccer games. Portland has a problem with drugs. This is because of mental health problems. The weather in Portland is also a problem. It is often rainy and gray. The city also has a problem with people who do not have a home. The city has good services for these people, but they are not enough. Some people in the city do not know what to do with this problem. They are happy with the city's weirdness, but not with its problems.

The mountains are always there. They stand in the north, watching the sun rise and set every day. They do not change. They are strong and calm. They do not change even when I am busy with my life and work.

When I am very stressed, the mountains remind me to stop and rest. They give me strength to go on. I moved here when I started college. The mountains north of campus were beautiful and caught my attention. The university has many nice buildings, ponds, and trees. But the mountains are special. The rest of the town is nice too. There are many cafes where I studied and drank coffee. I can walk or take the bus to the downtown area. The buildings there are old and pleasant. They make me feel calm. But the mountains have a strong presence. The town is a mix of calm and busy places. It is like a small town and a big city combined. I can walk to the library to find peace. The library is quiet and calm.

I have happy and sad memories in this town. I walked with friends in the park and went to the movie theater. The ponds are a good place to think and cry. I have had my share of crying there. I like to watch the animals living by the pond. They remind me of my own life and purpose. I walked past the pond and park to the main street. The sun was shining and I saw the mountains. They were as strong and calm as always. They reminded me to keep going.

If you visit Bensonhurst, Brooklyn, you will have no problem finding it. Public transportation is easy to use. Many people in New York City use it. Bensonhurst is a busy neighborhood. You will feel like you are in New York City. There are many Asian stores in the area. This is because many Asians live there. You will see an Asian store on almost every block. The stores sell food and do laundry. People like these stores because the food is good, prices are low, and it is easy to go there. 

There are four Asian stores near me. You can walk to them in two minutes. This makes it easy to buy food. Bensonhurst is not only Asian. Many different kinds of people live there. They are from many countries. Many Asian people own businesses in the neighborhood. There is a nice park near me. It has basketball courts, a big field for soccer or baseball, and a playground for kids. This park is fun for everyone. 

The neighborhood is not very tall. There are no big buildings. Most people live in small houses or apartments. The people are nice, but they can be noisy. You will hear cars playing loud music as they drive by. People also drive fast, which can wake you up. If you visit at night, be careful. This neighborhood is safe, but some people can cause trouble. I have had problems in the past, but that was a long time ago. There are also thieves who take packages. People do not clean up after their dogs. You will see dog waste on the street every day. Be careful and keep your shoes clean!

I do not like my sidewalk. Where I live, everything goes downhill. My house is at the top of a big hill. People call it the "exercise hill" because runners like to run up it. There is no sidewalk on my street. Everyone walks on the road. The road has many holes and is not safe to drive on. There are many wires above the road. They look old and broken. It rains a lot in my area. The wind breaks the wires and causes trouble. There are many big trees everywhere. But people do not like the trees. They want to cut them down because they block the ocean view. That is why houses are built high on the hill. They have big windows to see the ocean. It is beautiful at sunset. The water shines and the sky turns orange. But it is often cloudy and damp. Moss grows on everything. It even grows on my car. I left my car outside for a month. When I went to use it, it was green and covered in moss. I had to clean it for a long time. There are not many children in my area. There is a school nearby, but most people are old and retired. They have dogs instead of kids. I see dogs in people's yards or running in the street. If you do not close your door or window, dogs may come in. I once found a dog in my house and had to chase it out. There are many rabbits in my area. They are big and dig up plants and lawns. My cats like to hunt them. We also see many birds like sparrows and hummingbirds. Sometimes a hawk or eagle flies by. But the crows chase it away. There are no stores near me. But if you walk down to the waterfront, there are restaurants that serve fresh fish. The bay is not very wide. You can see the other side even on cloudy days.

I live in a small town in Tennessee. My house is on a street that connects two state highways. We have a bit more traffic on our street, but it is quiet. Not many people move in or out of our neighborhood. I know most of my neighbors. They work in their yards and do daily chores. In the winter, we sled down a hill on our street. Our house is on a corner, so we see people coming and going. We notice new cars. Some neighbors walk for exercise or their dogs. Children play on their bikes. I work from my house. My wife and I have two daughters. We get outside and play even when it rains. We grill in our backyard. It smells good. People cut their grass often. We have many trees, so it is cool and shady. But we have a lot of leaves in the fall. We must clean up the leaves every year. I like the smell of burning leaves. It means fall is here. We have not had much winter lately, so it feels like fall is long. I like to work on my truck in my garage. It is at the back of my house. I do not use the front door much. I like to be close to the neighborhood when I work in the garage. On holidays, we visit with our neighbors who are not from around here. We have a few cars parked in front of our house. I like living here. If it were not a through street, it would be perfect.

I live in a neighborhood in the desert. There is a lot of dirt. You see brown everywhere. When you see a green lawn, it is special. People work hard to keep it green. 

When I first moved here, the houses were far apart. Now there are more houses. It looks like a city. But it is still a small town. Most people are friendly. Some are not. My neighborhood is a good place to live. There are friendly old people. I like it here.

There are not many stores with many choices. You can find basic things like food and clothes. If you want special food, you have to go to another town. Many people work in construction. The town is still growing. There are many empty spaces. I like it the way it is now. I moved from a big city to a small town. I do not want to go back.

I work in construction. I install drywall and T-bars. I like the animals in the desert. People come here to see the desert's beauty. The desert is a hard place to live. It has many types of animals. We should learn about the animals so we can live with them peacefully.

My children like the animals. They are outside now, trying to catch lizards and bugs. We like living here. Victorville is a good place for families to visit. You can see the desert in a new way. There is a fair every year. You should come and visit in the summer. You can also go to Wrightwood to see the snow and ski. If you like history and nature, visit the Victor Valley Museum. It has rocks, old bones, and things from Native American people.

My neighborhood is a little different. It is the college campus where I live. My community is the people in my dorm. I also consider the rest of the campus my neighborhood. My campus neighborhood is not like most neighborhoods. It has some things in common, however.

Let's talk about the buildings in my neighborhood. There are three kinds of houses. Some are apartments. These buildings have 2 to 4 people in each room. There are 4 to 6 rooms on each floor. Most buildings have 2 floors. This means there are about 20 people in each building. Some houses are for rent. They have 2 to 4 bedrooms. Few students live in these houses. Most students live in dorms. These are the most common type of housing. A few students share a room.

My school is proud of its diversity. People from many cultures and ages live in my neighborhood. Some staff members live in houses. New students live in dorms. Older students live in apartments. Now, let's talk about the stores and park in my neighborhood. My school is like its own neighborhood. It has many stores. They sell food, clothes, and other things. The park is a place for everyone. It is clean and safe because of the people in my neighborhood.

I have lived in this neighborhood for 10 years. I was sad when I first moved here from Riverdale. I missed my friends and family, but my mom and dad wanted a better life for me and my sister. They wanted a better house, a good high school, and a safe place.

Over time, I made new friends and new enemies. I never really got to know my neighbors until I met Mr. Glen and his family. They are nice people. We consider them like family. I enjoyed their wedding. It was fun.

I remember Mr. Glen's wife threw away her crutch, and I caught the strap. We all danced and had a good time. I played with their daughter Marsharii. I hope she's happy now.

The neighborhood is like a maze, but I have a GPS now. I can explore it. I like to play video games with my friends Kason and Curtis. We also play outside and go to the park. It's peaceful there. I like to practice my balance with sticks from Home Depot. I also have a wooden sword.

There is a basketball and tennis court. I used to play tennis with my dad and Mr. Graves. They made us work hard, but it was fun. I think I've had a good time in this neighborhood. I am excited to see what the future holds.

I like my neighborhood because it is close to my college. I can walk to class. There are many apartment buildings in my neighborhood. Some buildings have restaurants and bars. These places are fun and not very expensive. One bar changed its name recently. It is more expensive, but the staff and drinks are good.

Many people live in my neighborhood. They are mostly students or people who do not make a lot of money. The rent is not high. There is an elementary school nearby. Many children live in the area.

I do not know my neighbors well. They smoke a lot of marijuana. The manager of my building put a device to take away bad smells outside their door. My boyfriend and I think this is funny. It is like a joke.

The buildings in my area are old, but they may have new insides. Some buildings near the campus are new. But I do not like them. They were not built well, but the rent is high. I think this is unfair.

There is a cheap restaurant near my home. They serve food on paper plates. Most of their food is cooked in a microwave. Across from this restaurant is a gas station. This is a place people do not like to work.

The road near my home was fixed with money from the city. Now there is a wide sidewalk and many trees. My area is more beautiful now.

My apartment building has many trees around it. The manager cut some of the trees, so there are stumps. There are more trees near my home than in another street. Behind my building is a line of trees and another set of apartments.

I live on 42nd Street. Behind me is 43rd Street. This street is not as nice. The sidewalk is broken and the buildings look old. There are many trees on this street. Maybe the trees hide the bad buildings. There has been some crime near my home. But it happens in other places too. I like my neighborhood. It is close to my college. There is a store and a bus stop near my home. I can easily go to the store or downtown.

My neighborhood is made up of houses that look like single houses. But they are connected. Each house is painted yellow, with a white porch and a green roof. Most people know each other. We stand together at the end of a street some evenings. We talk and watch the children play outside. It is a happy time in a busy world. It is like living in the past.

We live near fields and trees. The sky is blue and there are white clouds. We have beautiful weather usually. But sometimes we get bad weather. Last night we had a tornado warning. We had to go to a safe place. I was in the bathtub with my little dog. My other dog stayed in the living room. He was very nervous. 

After the storm, the road was hot. The hail had melted on the ground. The sun came out and it started to rain. We saw a beautiful rainbow. I took a picture with my camera. My friends and family liked the picture. It made them happy. The street was quiet for a while after the storm. Then people started coming home. We went back to normal. 

I like my neighborhood. It is a nice place to live. I have a small apartment with two rooms and two bathrooms. But my apartment is not the same as my neighbors'. Some apartments are very small. I like to walk in the big field behind my house. I see deer and hear a big frog singing. It is a good place to live. We are close to the city of Charlotte. We have roosters singing in the morning. We also have a donkey at a nearby farm. He brays in the evening. I am lucky to live here.

I moved here when I was about to start eighth grade. At first, I had a hard time making friends. But then I got close to two people who lived near me. They do not live here anymore, but I still remember them. Most of the people who lived here when I arrived are still here. My neighborhood is like many American suburban neighborhoods. There are many two-story houses. Every weekend, I hear kids playing outside when it is warm. The neighborhood is usually quiet most days. I have never had a problem with anyone in the neighborhood. They leave you alone unless you need help. I have ordered packages online and never had a problem with them being stolen. I feel safe in my neighborhood. There is a park nearby. I have many good memories there. I played basketball, football, and baseball with my friends. I also got hurt there once when someone hit me in the nose playing football. But I like the good memories more. Now, I go to the park to spend time with my younger cousin's kids. They like to play on swings and slides. The park makes me feel happy and sad at the same time. My neighborhood is different from others. You can find many kinds of food nearby. There are Chinese, Indian, Mexican, and Italian restaurants within one mile. But many people use food delivery apps like GrubHub and DoorDash now. There are also many fast food places and pizza shops. We have many stores with everything we need. There are dry cleaners, a pharmacy, and a grocery store. Some stores are special, like an Indian store where you can buy Indian food or ingredients to make it. I like my neighborhood. Reading about bad things that happen to people with their neighbors makes me happy to have a good one.

My neighborhood is a small town in South Carolina. It is not special, but it is important. Johnston is called the Peach Capital of the World. Many peach trees and cattle are in this area. Houses are far apart from each other. They are usually two stories high with metal or gray roofs to keep cool in the hot summer.

There are no stores near me, but in the center of town, there is a stop light. This is where you can find stores. There are three places to eat fast food: Hong Kong, a Chinese restaurant; Fiesta, a Mexican restaurant; and Gary's, a burger place. There used to be a pizza place, but it closed.

There is a small pharmacy called Maxwell and Halford Drug. People go there for Cherry Coca-Cola. There is also a grocery store called IGA. But people often go to Walmart in another town to buy most of their groceries.

The most popular store is Dollar General. It sells many things and is always busy. There is a furniture store called Possibilities Furniture. It has been in Johnston for a long time. They deliver furniture to your house. Next to the furniture store is a place called Clark's Cuts and Kennels. They take care of animals.

There is a school called Johnston Elementary School. Children go there until they are in fifth grade. Then they go to another town for middle and high school. We are making a new park. But right now, there is nothing much to do in Johnston. There are no movie theaters, bowling alleys, or playgrounds. But it is a nice town.

I first heard about my area from a podcast about people who are missing. It was a surprise. Many apartments in the area cost over one thousand dollars a month. I had not heard about this story before. Neither had my friends. Maybe this is what makes it hard. I know some of my friends feel sad at night. Things are expensive, but we have learned to save money. We like things that are cheap. We like the smell of old toys and clothing. When you grow up, you do not smell as much. Some people start to smoke. Some people get used to the situation. But the flea market is always there. The smell of old magazines on a piano is strong. It stays in the leather even after you wash it. There are three second-hand stores near my home. You can walk to them. If you start on one side, you can visit two charity stores, a library, a rare book store and a special shop. The streets are crowded in the city center. Cars and people are everywhere in the morning. But inside the stores, it is quiet. It is a good place to spend an afternoon. Many people come to the city every year. It is a city that is growing. One of the big companies that sells things online and delivers them is based here. The city is still getting better. It reminds me of New York. Everyone is busy with their own goals. Nobody usually asks for help. You can be alone if you want. People will leave you alone. This is different from the South, where people care about each other. Here, you do not ask personal questions. You can keep to yourself if you want to. The city is lively. There are musicians living next door and singers upstairs. There is always something happening. We do not feel like strangers in our apartment building. We are like friends. We help each other when we need it. We celebrate birthdays and help each other when we are sad. I like my neighbors. They are kind to me. I try to be kind to them too. I clean after myself and leave food for them. They do the same. We bring mail to each other. It's nice to see them. I think they like my company as much as I like theirs. I live in a big building. It is not very human. But my neighbors make me feel like I am not alone.

I live in a common type of neighborhood. It is like many others. My neighborhood is in a suburban area. You can see this when you look at the houses. They are all the same. The homeowner's association makes sure they are kept in good condition. The front yards are similar. There is a small patch of grass, some small stones, and a short driveway. The houses are usually one story, but some are two stories.

The roads in our neighborhood are very good. They are new and smooth. You do not see many potholes. The neighborhood has many things that make it nice to live here. We have community pools that anyone can use. There are walking trails where you can walk your dog or take a walk by yourself. We have a lot of space, so you can walk around the neighborhood to get exercise.

Most people in the neighborhood are old. But we also have some middle-aged and young people. The neighborhood is safe. Everyone looks out for each other. We have many things that people need, like a mall. It is not very big, but it works. We have many stores, including ones that sell healthy food and ones that have cheap things.

It takes 15 minutes to drive to the city. But when you get there, you can find many stores. We have many nice things in our neighborhood. The neighborhood is safe and well-maintained. We have pools and walking trails. But we do not have stores right next door. You can just drive to the city and find what you need.

I live in a small town in the Midwest. It is near a big city. My neighborhood is on the east side of the town. It is not the best area. Many houses are rented or owned by people who do not have a lot of money. But it is not a bad place. My neighbors are friendly. They say hello when I walk down the street.

Crime is a little higher in my neighborhood. There have been some bad crimes in the past. Some people have been shot and killed. But we are lucky. We have not been hurt. Sometimes, things go missing from our porch if we leave them outside.

The town I live in is affected by a big problem called the opioid epidemic. Many people have died from a strong drug called fentanyl. But we have help. There are places where people can go to get better. They can learn to stop using the drug.

My son goes to a good school. The teachers and staff are kind. He has friends and likes to go to school. The school gives free breakfast and lunch to all students. No one goes hungry. The town is trying to make our neighborhood look better. They have fixed roads and parks. But they have not done much on our side of town.

I like living here. People are friendly, the schools are good, and there are stores to buy things we need. Our home is not expensive, but it is comfortable. I have lived here for 16 years. I do not want to move.

My neighborhood is special. It is on a hill. Many old buildings are there. They have history. I live in a 7-story apartment building near an old theater. A bar is a block away. People go there on warm summer nights. Many people want to go in, so there is a long line. A park is a few blocks away. It is big. People walk around the park on a concrete path. There are stairs in the wall. In the winter, homeless people put up tents. They are close together. They keep warm. They are close to a center where people can bathe and shower.

I like my city. I like the people. Many years ago, this was a bad place. There was much violence. The government and police came to clean the streets. The people remember. They still tell stories about it. The people work hard to keep the neighborhood clean. They care about what happens in their city.

Some people say you should not walk in my neighborhood at night if you are white. I think this is not true. I am light-skinned, but I feel like I am one of them. I know the neighborhood is rough. But I feel safe there. People are kind. A laundromat owner helped me when I was in trouble. Someone gave me money when I was cold and grey. They said I was beautiful.

This is my home. I feel alive when I walk in the neighborhood at night. I meet people who are kind. They are my friends.

I live in a small town in Michigan, in the United States. This is a place where farmland and small tourist cities are common. You will not find big city malls or big stores like Walmart or Target. If you want to go somewhere, you must use a car. But my town is one of the most beautiful places in the world. We have a lot of water around us. Beautiful Lake Michigan is on one side, and Lake Charlevoix is on the other. You can find a beach to swim in almost everywhere you go.

My neighborhood is like a small town. Houses are not close together. They are not the same. Some houses are old and some are new. Many houses have basements. You can see the basements from the road. Most houses have aluminum siding. You can see many different colors in the houses around my home. Every house has a yard. Some yards have trampolines and playsets for kids. Some people have gardens and fences for their animals.

The people who live here are hard workers. They work to make a living and raise their families. On any day, you will see kids playing outside and people walking their dogs or riding bicycles. Neighbors know each other and can tell who belongs and who does not. Everyone is friendly and says hello to each other. The lawns are well cared for. Leaves are not piled up on the lawns. The grass is cut and kept under control. People take care of their plants and bushes.

This is not a beautiful neighborhood that you think is very nice when you see it. But it is a good place to live. It is quiet and peaceful and safe. You can walk to the police station and the health department. The city's recycling center is nearby. We also have baseball and softball fields where you can hear the announcers calling the game. Our small airport is near the fields. You can hear the small planes flying and landing. You can walk to get ice cream or go downtown from my neighborhood. My kids can ride their bikes to the park, which is only a few blocks away. This is a great place to live.
